# Local dev: omit VITE_API_BASE_URL (or leave empty) so the app calls same-origin `/api/*`
# and Vite proxies to the Bun API (see vite.config.ts). No CORS needed on the API for that setup.
#
# Alternative: set a full URL (e.g. http://127.0.0.1:3000) and set CORS_ALLOW_ORIGIN on apps/api
# to match your Vite origin exactly (http://localhost:5173 vs http://127.0.0.1:5173 differ).
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=
